product item\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:48px 24px 0px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-image\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;text-align:center;\\"><img src=\\"https://i.ibb.co/3TMrgVk/samsung-galaxy-a32-128gb-6gb-blue-9.jpg\\" alt=\\"samsung-galaxy-a32-128gb-6gb-blue-9.jpg\\" /></div><div class=\\"feature-description\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-content\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\\"><h3 style=\\"margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:auto;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;padding-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:0px;width:397.594px;\\">Hold A Galaxy In Your Hand</h3><ul><li>Samsung Galaxy A32 is thin and extremely light.</li><li>Weighting only 184g, it can be used in one hand for an extended period with ease.</li><li>FHD+ Super AMOLED Infinity-U display provides unconstrained, immersive viewing.</li><li>Galaxy A32 offers eye care display certified from SDC.</li><li>This filters out harmful blue light to protect your vision, prevent eye fatigue and even help you fall asleep faster.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\\"product item\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:48px 24px 0px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-description\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-content\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\\"><h3 style=\\"margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:auto;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;padding-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:0px;width:397.594px;\\">Looks Good and Feels Even Better</h3><ul><li>90HZ refresh rate reduces motion blur and improves image quality whether you are watching video or playing games.</li><li>MediaTek Helio G80 octa-core processor provides faster performance for smoother and more responsive gaming.</li><li>During games, Priority Mode blocks incoming calls and all notifications except alarm.</li><li>Galaxy A32 comes equipped with 128GB ROM and 6GB RAM.</li><li>While supports up to 1TB of additional memory into the card for tons of extra storage.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\"feature-image\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;text-align:center;\\"><img src=\\"https://i.ibb.co/k6rtRyn/samsung-galaxy-a32-128gb-6gb-blue-7.jpg\\" alt=\\"samsung-galaxy-a32-128gb-6gb-blue-7.jpg\\" /></div></div><div class=\\"product item\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:48px 24px 0px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-image\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;text-align:center;\\"><img src=\\"https://i.ibb.co/pjgjxxV/samsung-galaxy-a32-camera.jpg\\" alt=\\"samsung-galaxy-a32-camera.jpg\\" /></div><div class=\\"feature-description\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-content\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\\"><h3 style=\\"margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:auto;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;padding-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:0px;width:397.594px;\\">Add More Perspective to Everything You Shoot</h3><ul><li>Samsung Galaxy A32 fits four rear and one front cameras into a single smartphone.</li><li>A 64MP rear main camera renders overlooked details in vivid splendor that transcends what your eyes see.</li><li>Similar to human eyesight, the 8MP Ultra Wide Camera sees the world with a 123-degree angle of view.</li><li>This lets you capture panoramic pictures and save bigger scenes in confined spaces.</li><li>Get in close with the 5MP Macro Camera and capture finest details with best clarity.</li><li>Depth camera with 5MP resolution provides artistic portrait effects.</li><li>Save your beloved scenes and record your own facial expressions with the 20MP front camera.</li><li>Its blur effect lets you snap stunning selfies that feature more you and less background.</li><li>While smart beauty feature facilitates impeccable selfies in different occasions.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\\"product item\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:48px 24px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-description\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;\\"><div class=\\"feature-content\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\\"><h3 style=\\"margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:auto;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;padding-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:0px;width:397.594px;\\">Looks Intelligent. Because It Is!</h3><ul><li>5000mAh battery frees you from the burden of untimely battery drain.</li><li>So you can enjoy unstoppable performance for up to 2 days.</li><li>With 15W fast charging, your phone quickly gets back to full power.</li><li>Power Saving Mode optimizes CPU resources and disables background data to conserve battery.</li><li>Enjoy quick and easy unlock with a simple touch on your screen.</li><li>Offering multi-layered security, Galaxy A32 defends your most sensitive information from malware and malicious threats.</li><li>While allows you to create a private, fully encrypted space that is only accessible with your fingerprint or password.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\\"feature-image\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;width:568px;text-align:center;\\"><img src=\\"https://i.ibb.co/M1MGCTV/samsung-galaxy-a32-battery.jpg\\" alt=\\"samsung-galaxy-a32-battery.jpg\\" /></div></div></div></div><div class=\\"item title allow active\\" style=\\"border-width:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;color:rgb(14,0,26);font-family:'ibm-plex-sans-arabic', sans-serif, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><div class=\\"data switch\\" style=\\"border-width:1px 0px 0px;border-top-style:solid;border-top-color:rgb(227,229,232);margin-bottom:0px;padding:24px;\\"><h4 style=\\"margin-bottom:0px;border:0px;vertical-align: