5267800f-4b7b-4983-aebe-e9bd8e587fc0	45bd6d0e-e9d6-4a1a-ae90-f5fbbcbf5682	1372dce9-5c2c-4d74-95bc-0b5210a55f26	{"ar": "ASUS ROG GL702VS Gaming Laptop - Intel Core I7-7700HQ - 12GB RAM - 1TB HDD + 128GB SSD - 17.3\\" Full HD - 8GB GTX1070 GPU - Windows 10 - English Keyboard", "en": "ASUS ROG GL702VS Gaming Laptop - Intel Core I7-7700HQ - 12GB RAM - 1TB HDD + 128GB SSD - 17.3\\" Full HD - 8GB GTX1070 GPU - Windows 10 - English Keyboard"}	{"ar": "<p>COMPACT AND POTENT</p><p>ROG Strix GL702 packs the latest 7th-generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 processor and NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX1070 graphics in a compact and lightweight design, fully equipped with a stunning 120 Hz G-SYNCâ„¢ panel. ROG Strix GL702 enables users to enjoy high-end gaming from anywhere.</p><p>MATCHLESS PERFORMANCE</p><p>Experience unmatched performance with ROG Strix GL702's 7th-generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 quad-core processor combined with a discrete VR-Ready NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX 1070 graphics with full MicrosoftÂ® DirectXÂ® 12 support. The latest hardware gives you efficient, powerful performance for heavy gaming or productive multitasking such as live streaming and video editing.</p><p>Ultimate Gaming Platform</p><p>Take on today's challenging, graphics-intensive games without missing a beat. GeForce GTX 1070-powered notebooks deliver the incredible speed and power of NVIDIA Pascalâ„¢â€”the most advanced GPU architecture ever createdâ€”for truly revolutionary gaming and VR performance.</p><p>Performance</p><p>The GeForce GTX 1070 GPU is created with high-speed FinFET technology and supports DirectX 12 features to deliver fast, smooth, power-efficient gaming notebook experiences. You can count on an amazing experience in every applicationâ€”including performance in AAA and immersive VR Ready games that's up to 3X faster than with previous-generation GPUs.</p><p>The Latest Gaming Technologies</p><p>Get the power to drive next-generation displays, including VR, ultra-high-resolution, and multiple monitors. And bring more realism to every game with NVIDIA GameWorksâ„¢ technologies that deliver a true cinematic experience and amazing new NVIDIA Anselâ„¢ that enables 360-degree in-game captures you can view in VR.</p><p>VR Ready</p><p>Discover next-generation VR performance, the lowest latency, and plug-and-play compatibility with leading headsetsâ€”driven by NVIDIA VRWorksâ„¢ technologies. VR audio, physics, and haptics let you hear and feel every moment.</p><p>STUNNING 120 HZ WIDE-VIEW PANEL WITH NVIDIA G-SYNCâ„¢</p><p>ROG GL702 is equipped with a super-fast 120Hz wide-view panel that supports NVIDIA G-SYNCâ„¢ technology for fast-paced games. GL702 features NVIDIA G-SYNCâ„¢ display technology which synchronizes its display's refresh rate with its graphics card for ultra-smooth visuals. G-SYNCâ„¢ helps avoid lag, minimizes frame-rate stutter, and eliminates visual tearing. It delivers the smoothest and fastest gaming graphics â€” all without affecting system performance!</p><p>*Actual specification may vary according to configuration.</p><p>IMMERSIVE VIRTUAL REALITY</p><p>The VR Ready NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX 1070 GPU boosts speed and power efficiency for brilliant performance in Virtual Reality. Enjoy immersive virtual reality that is smooth, low-latency, and stutter-free.</p><p>GAMING ON-THE-GO</p><p>With a profile measuring just 30.4mm and tipping the scales at a light weight 2.9kg, ROG Strix GL702 has an ultra-portable. design that fits snugly in a messenger bag or backpack. Whether you're waiting for your flight, kicking back at a cafÃ©, or at a LAN tournament, you can game just about anywhere!</p><p>MORE SCREEN, LESS BEZEL</p><p>ROG Strix GL702's display comes with a slimmed down bezel, measuring just 17mm on the top and 13mm on the sides, for a more pleasant and discreet viewing experience.</p><p>INTELLIGENT THERMAL DESIGN</p><p>The Hyper Cool Duo-Copper cooling system uses heat pipes and a dual fan system to cool the CPU and GPU independently. This design maximizes cooling efficiency to give ROG Strix GL702 the stability required for intense gaming marathons.</p><p>ANTI-GHOSTING KEYBOARD WITH 30-KEY ROLLOEVR</p><p>Anti-ghosting keys ensure your commands are instantaneously and correctly interpreted â€“ even if you hit up to 30 keys simultaneously.</p><p>A KEYBOARD DESIGNED FOR GAMING</p><p>Our tactile gaming keyboard also features ASUS-exclusive Overstroke technology, a stylish red backlight, specially designed WASD keys, and a deep 1.6mm travel distance. Our engineering team meticulously tests our keyboards for ultimate durability and reliability resulting in an expected lifetime of 10 million key presses. ROG Strix GL702 will arm you with a keyboard that you can trust.</p><p>INTELÂ® THUNDERBOLT 3 WITH USB TYPE-C</p><p>Onboard IntelÂ® Thunderboltâ„¢ technology gives you single-cable data and signal transmission rates of up to 40Gbps. ROG Strix GL702 gives you both Intel Thunderbolt and USB 3.1 Type-C for increased compatibility with your various devices.</p><p>*Actual specification may vary according to configuration</p><p>UP TO 32GB OF DDR4</p><p>ROG Strix GL702 is fitted with up to 32GB of DDR4 RAM, the latest standard in memory. Benefit from the improved speed, capacity, and lower power consumption of the newest generation to really boost your gaming experience.</p><p>SSD FOR SUPERFAST LOADING SPEEDS</p><p>NVMe PCIe x4 SSD gives you superfast data access speeds so you spend less time waiting. ROG Strix GL702 boots up faster, loads apps quicker, and gives you shorter in-game loading times so you stay immersed and focused on the game. Don't stop at a blazing fast SSD, equip your ROG Strix GL702 with up to a SATA 2TB 2.5' HDD for an abundance of storage space.</p><p>*Actual specification may vary according to configuration.</p><p>FILTER OUT ALL AMBIENT NOISE</p><p>The array microphones are designed to filter out ambient noise, which means that even if you're at a LAN party or in another loud environment, your voice will come through loud and clear.</p><p>SONIC STUDIO & SONIC RADAR</p><p>Sonic Studio and Sonic Radar deliver immersive gaming audio. Sonic Studio provides high quality in-game audio, as well as improved streaming and audio recording for perfect voice pickup and noise reduction. Sonic Radar helps you detect opponents through an on-screen overlay that shows the relative position of gunshots, footsteps and other in-game sound effects.</p><p>ROG GAMING CENTER</p><p>ROG Gaming Center allows you to launch ROG applications and easily access settings. Integrated applications include ROG Game First, XSplit Gamecaster, ROG MacroKey, and Splendid.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Technical Specifications:</p><p><br /></p><p>Processor</p><ul><li>IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 7700HQ Processor 2.8 GHz (6M Cache, up to 3.80 GHz, # of Cores: 4)</li><li>IntelÂ® HM175 Express Chipset<br /></li></ul>Memory<ul><li>Installed Memory: 12 GB DDR4 </li><li>Max Memory: up to 32 GB DDR4</li></ul>Display<ul><li></li><li>17.3\\" (3:2) LED backlit FHD (1920x1080) 75Hz Anti-Glare Panel with 72% NTSC with G-Sync </li></ul>Graphics<ul><li>Graphics Processor: NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX1070</li><li>Dedicated Memory: 8 GB DDR5</li></ul>Storage<ul><li>Storage Capacity: 1x 128GB PCIE SSD</li><li>1TB 7200RPM SATA HDD</li><li>Optical Drive: None</li></ul>Inputs and Outputs<ul><li>1 x COMBO audio jack </li><li>1 x USB 3.1 TYPE C port(s)</li><li>3 x USB 3.0 port(s) </li><li>1 x RJ45 LAN Jack for LAN insert </li><li>1 x HDMI </li><li>1 x mini Display Port</li><li>1 x Thunderbolt port </li><li>1 x SD card reader </li></ul>Audio<ul><li>Support Windows 10 Cortana </li><li>ASUS SonicMaster Premium Technology</li></ul>Hardware<ul><li>Camera: HD Web Camera</li><li>Keyboard: Illuminated Chiclet Keyboard (English Only, No Arabic Letters Engraved)</li></ul>Wireless/Networking<ul><li>BluetoothÂ® Technology: Built-in Bluetoothâ„¢ V4.1</li><li>Wi-Fi: Dual-band 802.11AC</li><li>LAN: 1 x RJ45 LAN Jack for LAN insert 10/100/1000</li></ul>Software<ul><li>Operating System: Windows 10 Home (64bit)</li></ul>Power<ul><li>Battery Type: 4 Cells 76 Whrs Battery</li></ul>Dimensions<ul><li>415 x 280 x 28 ~30 mm  (WxDxH)</li></ul>Weight<ul><li>2.9 kg</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>KEY FEATURES</p><ul><li>7th Generation Intel Core i7-7700HQ 2.8 GHz CPU</li><li>16 GB RAM, 1TB HDD + 256GB SSD</li><li>17.3\\" Full HD Screen</li><li>8GB NVIDIA GeForce GTX1080 GPU</li><li>Connectivity: Wi-Fi 802.11a/b/g/n/ac, Bluetooth 4.1</li><li>Operating System: Windows 10 Home</li><li>Illuminated Chicklet keyboard (English Only, No Arabic Letters Engraved)</li></ul><p>GENERAL</p>ModelGL702VS-AH73ColorCopper TitaniumProduction Country<p>SCREENDisplay Size (inches)17.3Display TypeFull HD|LED</p><p>PROCESSORProcessor TypeIntel Core i7Processor Speed (GHz)2.80</p><p>MEMORYRAM (GB)12Capacity (GB)1128</p><p>GRAPHICSGraphic RAM (GB)8</p><p>CONNECTIVITYConnectivityWi-Fi|Bluetooth|HDMI|USB 3.0|USB-C|USB 3.1</p><p>FEATURESOperating SystemWindows</p><p>DIMENSIONSProduct Dimensions415 x 280 x 28 ~30 mm</p>", "en": "<p>COMPACT AND POTENT</p><p>ROG Strix GL702 packs the latest 7th-generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 processor and NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX1070 graphics in a compact and lightweight design, fully equipped with a stunning 120 Hz G-SYNCâ„¢ panel. ROG Strix GL702 enables users to enjoy high-end gaming from anywhere.</p><p>MATCHLESS PERFORMANCE</p><p>Experience unmatched performance with ROG Strix GL702's 7th-generation IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 quad-core processor combined with a discrete VR-Ready NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX 1070 graphics with full MicrosoftÂ® DirectXÂ® 12 support. The latest hardware gives you efficient, powerful performance for heavy gaming or productive multitasking such as live streaming and video editing.</p><p>Ultimate Gaming Platform</p><p>Take on today's challenging, graphics-intensive games without missing a beat. GeForce GTX 1070-powered notebooks deliver the incredible speed and power of NVIDIA Pascalâ„¢â€”the most advanced GPU archite