g, ROG Strix GL702 has an ultra-portable. design that fits snugly in a messenger bag or backpack. Whether you're waiting for your flight, kicking back at a cafÃ©, or at a LAN tournament, you can game just about anywhere!</p><p>MORE SCREEN, LESS BEZEL</p><p>ROG Strix GL702's display comes with a slimmed down bezel, measuring just 17mm on the top and 13mm on the sides, for a more pleasant and discreet viewing experience.</p><p>INTELLIGENT THERMAL DESIGN</p><p>The Hyper Cool Duo-Copper cooling system uses heat pipes and a dual fan system to cool the CPU and GPU independently. This design maximizes cooling efficiency to give ROG Strix GL702 the stability required for intense gaming marathons.</p><p>ANTI-GHOSTING KEYBOARD WITH 30-KEY ROLLOEVR</p><p>Anti-ghosting keys ensure your commands are instantaneously and correctly interpreted â€“ even if you hit up to 30 keys simultaneously.</p><p>A KEYBOARD DESIGNED FOR GAMING</p><p>Our tactile gaming keyboard also features ASUS-exclusive Overstroke technology, a stylish red backlight, specially designed WASD keys, and a deep 1.6mm travel distance. Our engineering team meticulously tests our keyboards for ultimate durability and reliability resulting in an expected lifetime of 10 million key presses. ROG Strix GL702 will arm you with a keyboard that you can trust.</p><p>INTELÂ® THUNDERBOLT 3 WITH USB TYPE-C</p><p>Onboard IntelÂ® Thunderboltâ„¢ technology gives you single-cable data and signal transmission rates of up to 40Gbps. ROG Strix GL702 gives you both Intel Thunderbolt and USB 3.1 Type-C for increased compatibility with your various devices.</p><p>*Actual specification may vary according to configuration</p><p>UP TO 32GB OF DDR4</p><p>ROG Strix GL702 is fitted with up to 32GB of DDR4 RAM, the latest standard in memory. Benefit from the improved speed, capacity, and lower power consumption of the newest generation to really boost your gaming experience.</p><p>SSD FOR SUPERFAST LOADING SPEEDS</p><p>NVMe PCIe x4 SSD gives you superfast data access speeds so you spend less time waiting. ROG Strix GL702 boots up faster, loads apps quicker, and gives you shorter in-game loading times so you stay immersed and focused on the game. Don't stop at a blazing fast SSD, equip your ROG Strix GL702 with up to a SATA 2TB 2.5' HDD for an abundance of storage space.</p><p>*Actual specification may vary according to configuration.</p><p>FILTER OUT ALL AMBIENT NOISE</p><p>The array microphones are designed to filter out ambient noise, which means that even if you're at a LAN party or in another loud environment, your voice will come through loud and clear.</p><p>SONIC STUDIO & SONIC RADAR</p><p>Sonic Studio and Sonic Radar deliver immersive gaming audio. Sonic Studio provides high quality in-game audio, as well as improved streaming and audio recording for perfect voice pickup and noise reduction. Sonic Radar helps you detect opponents through an on-screen overlay that shows the relative position of gunshots, footsteps and other in-game sound effects.</p><p>ROG GAMING CENTER</p><p>ROG Gaming Center allows you to launch ROG applications and easily access settings. Integrated applications include ROG Game First, XSplit Gamecaster, ROG MacroKey, and Splendid.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Technical Specifications:</p><p><br /></p><p>Processor</p><ul><li>IntelÂ® Coreâ„¢ i7 7700HQ Processor 2.8 GHz (6M Cache, up to 3.80 GHz, # of Cores: 4)</li><li>IntelÂ® HM175 Express Chipset<br /></li></ul>Memory<ul><li>Installed Memory: 12 GB DDR4 </li><li>Max Memory: up to 32 GB DDR4</li></ul>Display<ul><li></li><li>17.3\\" (3:2) LED backlit FHD (1920x1080) 75Hz Anti-Glare Panel with 72% NTSC with G-Sync </li></ul>Graphics<ul><li>Graphics Processor: NVIDIAÂ® GeForceÂ® GTX1070</li><li>Dedicated Memory: 8 GB DDR5</li></ul>Storage<ul><li>Storage Capacity: 1x 128GB PCIE SSD</li><li>1TB 7200RPM SATA HDD</li><li>Optical Drive: None</li></ul>Inputs and Outputs<ul><li>1 x COMBO audio jack </li><li>1 x USB 3.1 TYPE C port(s)</li><li>3 x USB 3.0 port(s) </li><li>1 x RJ45 LAN Jack for LAN insert </li><li>1 x HDMI </li><li>1 x mini Display Port</li><li>1 x Thunderbolt port </li><li>1 x SD card reader </li></ul>Audio<ul><li>Support Windows 10 Cortana </li><li>ASUS SonicMaster Premium Technology</li></ul>Hardware<ul><li>Camera: HD Web Camera</li><li>Keyboard: Illuminated Chiclet Keyboard (English Only, No Arabic Letters Engraved)</li></ul>Wireless/Networking<ul><li>BluetoothÂ® Technology: Built-in Bluetoothâ„¢ V4.1</li><li>Wi-Fi: Dual-band 802.11AC</li><li>LAN: 1 x RJ45 LAN Jack for LAN insert 10/100/1000</li></ul>Software<ul><li>Operating System: Windows 10 Home (64bit)</li></ul>Power<ul><li>Battery Type: 4 Cells 76 Whrs Battery</li></ul>Dimensions<ul><li>415 x 280 x 28 ~30 mm  (WxDxH)</li></ul>Weight<ul><li>2.9 kg</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>KEY FEATURES</p><ul><li>7th Generation Intel Core i7-7700HQ 2.8 GHz CPU</li><li>16 GB RAM, 1TB HDD + 256GB SSD</li><li>17.3\\" Full HD Screen</li><li>8GB NVIDIA GeForce GTX1080 GPU</li><li>Connectivity: Wi-Fi 802.11a/b/g/n/ac, Bluetooth 4.1</li><li>Operating System: Windows 10 Home</li><li>Illuminated Chicklet keyboard (English Only, No Arabic Letters Engraved)</li></ul><p>GENERAL</p>ModelGL702VS-AH73ColorCopper TitaniumProduction Country<p>SCREENDisplay Size (inches)17.3Display TypeFull HD|LED</p><p>PROCESSORProcessor TypeIntel Core i7Processor Speed (GHz)2.80</p><p>MEMORYRAM (GB)12Capacity (GB)1128</p><p>GRAPHICSGraphic RAM (GB)8</p><p>CONNECTIVITYConnectivityWi-Fi|Bluetooth|HDMI|USB 3.0|USB-C|USB 3.1</p><p>FEATURESOperating SystemWindows</p><p>DIMENSIONSProduct Dimensions415 x 280 x 28 ~30 mm</p>"}	asus-rog-gl702vs-gaming-laptop-intel-core-i7-7700hq-12gb-ram-1tb-hdd-128gb-ssd-17-3-full-hd-8gb-gtx1070-gpu-windows-10-english-keyboard-1258	39999.00	\N	\N	\N	1	5	active	f	0	2026-06-14 06:34:16.385	2026-06-14 06:42:03.932	\N	\N
