oto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><img src=\\"https://static.jumia.com.eg/cms/external/pet/SA024EL1E5N4SNAFAMZ/ca796788af3a7db7e976c6c87920347d.jpg\\" alt=\\"image\\" /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Designed to expand your world of entertainment and gaming even further for the ultimate experience. Its optimal 5.0â€ display is just the right size to view whatâ€™s on screen for maximum enjoyment.</p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Selfies that shine</p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><img src=\\"https://static.jumia.com.eg/cms/external/pet/SA024EL1E5N4SNAFAMZ/7994061d264f9a1953cf5591de613164.jpg\\" alt=\\"image\\" /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style