t-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Power extended</p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><img src=\\"https://static.jumia.com.eg/cms/external/pet/SA024EL1E5N4SNAFAMZ/1c20452e67c3a4b7646cc8978349d074.jpg\\" alt=\\"image\\" /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Now with even longer lasting battery power to pack in more multimedia and keep gamers in the action. Maximum Power Saving Mode turns off all background running apps to drastically minimise battery consumption.</p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><h2 style=\\"font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;margin-top:17px;margin-bottom:8.5px;font-size:14px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Technical Specifications:</h2><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><br /></p><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Display</p><ul><li>Display Size: 5.0 inches (~66.0% screen-to-body ratio)</li><li>Display Resolution: 540 x 960 pixels (~220 ppi pixel density)</li><li>Display Type: Capacitive touchscreen, 16M colors</li><li>Multitouch: Yes</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Camera</p><ul><li>Back Camera: 8 MegaPixel, f/2.2, autofocus, LED flash</li><li>Features: Geo-tagging</li><li>Video: Yes, 720p@30fps</li><li>Front Camera: 5 MegaPixel, f/2.2</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Processor</p><ul><li>Chipset: Mediatek MT6737T</li><li>CPU: Quad-core 1.4 GHz Cortex-A53</li><li>GPU: Mali-T720MP2</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Memory</p><ul><li>System Memory: 1.5 GB RAM</li><li>Internal Memory: 8 GB storage</li><li>Card Slot: microSD, up to 128 GB (uses SIM 2 slot)</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Operating System</p><ul><li>Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Sound</p><ul><li>Alert types: Vibration, MP3, WAV ringtones</li><li>Loud Speaker: Yes</li><li>3.5 mm Audio Jack: Yes</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">General</p><ul><li>2G Network: GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 - SIM 1 & SIM 2</li><li>3G Network: HSDPA 850 / 900 / 1900 / 2100</li><li>4G Network: LTE B1(2100), B3(1800), B5(850), B7(2600), B8(900), B20(800)</li><li>SIM: Dual SIM (Micro-SIM) or Single Micro SIM + Micro SD Card</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Data</p><ul><li>GPRS: Yes</li><li>EDGE: Yes</li><li>Speed: HSPA 21.1/5.76 Mbps</li><li>WLAN: Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot</li><li>Bluetooth: Yes, v4.2</li><li>USB: Yes, microUSB v2.0</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Features</p><ul><li>Sensors: Accelerometer, Proximity</li><li>Messaging: SMS (threaded view), MMS, Email, Push Mail, IM</li><li>Browser: HTML</li><li>Radio: FM radio</li><li>GPS: Yes, with A-GPS, GLONASS</li><li>Java: No</li><li>Document viewer</li><li>Photo viewer/editor</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Multimedia</p><ul><li>Audio: MP3/WAV/eAAC+/Flac player</li><li>Video: MP4/H.264 player</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Power</p><ul><li>Battery: Removable Li-Ion 2600 mAh battery</li></ul><p style=\\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:8.5px;color:rgb(96,96,96);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\">Body</p><ul><li>Dimensions: 144.8 x 72.1 x 8.9 mm</li><li>Weight: 160 g</li></ul><div class=\\"list -features\\" style=\\"margin-bottom:40px;color:rgb(85,85,85);font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\\"><div class=\\"title\\" style=\\"font-size:16px;line-height:20px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(170,170,170);margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px 0px 10px;text-transform:uppercase;\\">KEY FEATURES</div><ul><li>5.0\\" Capacitive Touch Screen</li><li>8 GB Storage, MicroSD up to 128 GB</li><li>8 MP Back Camera, 5 MP Front Camera</li><li>Quad-core 1.4 GHz CPU, 1.5 GB RAM</li><li>Android OS, v6.0.1 (Marshmallow)</li><li>Li-Ion 2600mAh battery, Dual SIM</li></ul></div><div class=\\"osh-table -no-border\\" style=\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);width:710px;color:rgb(96,96,96);table-layout:fixed;margin-top:40px;font-family:Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:12px;\\"><div class=\\"caption\\" style=\\"font-size:16px;line-height:20px;padding:0px 0px 10px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(170,170,170);text-transform:uppercase;\\">GENERAL</div><div class=\\"osh-row\\" style=\\"clear:both;\\"><div class=\\"osh-col -head\\" style=\\"padding:10px 20px 10px 0px;border-top:1px solid rgb(221,221,221);font-weight:700;color:rgb(0,0,0);width:177.273px;\\">SKU (config)</div><div class=\\"osh-col\\" style=\\"padding:10px 0px;border-top:1px solid rgb(221,221,221);\\">SA024EL1E5N4SNAFAMZ</div></div><div class=\\"osh-row\\" style=\\"clear:both;\\"><div class=\\"osh-col -head\\" style=\\"padding:10px 20px 10px 0px;border-top:1px solid rgb(221,221,221);font-weight:700;color:rgb(0,0,0);width:177.273px;\\">Model</div><div class=\\"osh-col\\" style=\\"padding:10px 0px;border-top:1px solid rgb(221,221,221);\\">Galaxy Grand Prime Plus</div></div><div class=\\"osh-row\\" style=\\"clear:both;\\"><div class=\\"osh-col -head\\"