26fd4fca-a1fd-4520-b933-89098470dc77	45bd6d0e-e9d6-4a1a-ae90-f5fbbcbf5682	b36d22ae-fa95-4284-8274-ee89f03b34dc	{"ar": "Beko RDNE340K22B No Frost Refrigerator, 340 Liter, 2 Doors - Black", "en": "Beko TS190210 S Freestanding Mini Bar Refrigerator, 87 Liters - Silver"}	{"ar": "<p><br /></p><p>High efficiency, high durability, less sound</p><p>If your refrigerator is making loud noises and consuming a lot of energy, now is the perfect time to make a change. Thanks to its innovative design, the ProSmart Inverter Compressor will provide faster cooling with less energy consumption and four times less noise than regular refrigerator compressors. It adapts to temperature changes quickly, maintaining food quality for a longer period while saving on your electricity bill, all at the same time.</p><p><br /></p><p>Two separate cooling systems do not transfer odor</p><p>It is difficult to leave fish in the refrigerator at the same time as a delicious cake without mixing its flavors. But with NeoFrost Dual Cooling technology, you will get two separate cooling systems for each compartment while maintaining ideal air flow and ideal temperatures in both the refrigerator and the freezer. As a result, the food will stay fresh longer without getting icy or changing its smell.</p><p><br /></p><p>Clear view from inside</p><p>Sometimes it's hard to see everything in the refrigerator, especially in the corners or behind the shelves. But Led Illumination presents a series of LED lights at the top of the refrigerator and on the side of each shelf so you can see everything clearly. It is also energy saving compared to normal lighting.</p><p><br /></p><p>The door direction is adjustable to suit your kitchen design</p><p>Some kitchen designs include opening the refrigerator doors to one side rather than the other. With Reversible Door technology, the door hinges can be placed on both the right and left of the refrigerator, so you can choose which side you want your refrigerator to open to. In addition, you can double your cooling capacity by placing two refrigerators next to each other with doors in opposite directions.</p>", "en": "<p>Color: Silver</p><p>Model: TS190210 S</p><p>Cooling Type: Defrost</p><p>Total Capacity In Litres: 87</p><p>Number Of Doors: 1</p><p>Interior Light</p><p>Freezer on Top</p><p>Refrigerator Dimensions: 81.8x47.5x53 cm</p>"}	beko-ts190210-s-freestanding-mini-bar-refrigerator-87-liters-silver-3076	10299.00	\N	\N	\N	0	5	active	f	0	2026-06-14 06:28:56.403	2026-06-14 06:42:04.455	\N	\N
