ac7e71ee-6f77-4034-b3a1-4a27893a7963	45bd6d0e-e9d6-4a1a-ae90-f5fbbcbf5682	b36d22ae-fa95-4284-8274-ee89f03b34dc	{"ar": "Beko RDNE340K22B No Frost Refrigerator, 340 Liter, 2 Doors - Black", "en": "Beko RDNE340K22B No Frost Refrigerator, 340 Liter, 2 Doors - Black"}	{"ar": "<p><br /></p><p>High efficiency, high durability, less sound</p><p>If your refrigerator is making loud noises and consuming a lot of energy, now is the perfect time to make a change. Thanks to its innovative design, the ProSmart Inverter Compressor will provide faster cooling with less energy consumption and four times less noise than regular refrigerator compressors. It adapts to temperature changes quickly, maintaining food quality for a longer period while saving on your electricity bill, all at the same time.</p><p><br /></p><p>Two separate cooling systems do not transfer odor</p><p>It is difficult to leave fish in the refrigerator at the same time as a delicious cake without mixing its flavors. But with NeoFrost Dual Cooling technology, you will get two separate cooling systems for each compartment while maintaining ideal air flow and ideal temperatures in both the refrigerator and the freezer. As a result, the food will stay fresh longer without getting icy or changing its smell.</p><p><br /></p><p>Clear view from inside</p><p>Sometimes it's hard to see everything in the refrigerator, especially in the corners or behind the shelves. But Led Illumination presents a series of LED lights at the top of the refrigerator and on the side of each shelf so you can see everything clearly. It is also energy saving compared to normal lighting.</p><p><br /></p><p>The door direction is adjustable to suit your kitchen design</p><p>Some kitchen designs include opening the refrigerator doors to one side rather than the other. With Reversible Door technology, the door hinges can be placed on both the right and left of the refrigerator, so you can choose which side you want your refrigerator to open to. In addition, you can double your cooling capacity by placing two refrigerators next to each other with doors in opposite directions.</p>", "en": "<p><br /></p><p>High efficiency, high durability, less sound</p><p>If your refrigerator is making loud noises and consuming a lot of energy, now is the perfect time to make a change. Thanks to its innovative design, the ProSmart Inverter Compressor will provide faster cooling with less energy consumption and four times less noise than regular refrigerator compressors. It adapts to temperature changes quickly, maintaining food quality for a longer period while saving on your electricity bill, all at the same time.</p><p><br /></p><p>Two separate cooling systems do not transfer odor</p><p>It is difficult to leave fish in the refrigerator at the same time as a delicious cake without mixing its flavors. But with NeoFrost Dual Cooling technology, you will get two separate cooling systems for each compartment while maintaining ideal air flow and ideal temperatures in both the refrigerator and the freezer. As a result, the food will stay fresh longer without getting icy or changing its smell.</p><p><br /></p><p>Clear view from inside</p><p>Sometimes it's hard to see everything in the refrigerator, especially in the corners or behind the shelves. But Led Illumination presents a series of LED lights at the top of the refrigerator and on the side of each shelf so you can see everything clearly. It is also energy saving compared to normal lighting.</p><p><br /></p><p>The door direction is adjustable to suit your kitchen design</p><p>Some kitchen designs include opening the refrigerator doors to one side rather than the other. With Reversible Door technology, the door hinges can be placed on both the right and left of the refrigerator, so you can choose which side you want your refrigerator to open to. In addition, you can double your cooling capacity by placing two refrigerators next to each other with doors in opposite directions.</p>"}	beko-rdne340k22b-no-frost-refrigerator-340-liter-2-doors-black-3077	27899.00	\N	\N	\N	0	5	active	f	0	2026-06-14 06:34:17.387	2026-06-14 06:42:04.456	\N	\N
1aee58bd-8a16-4048-9f95-57b2e3c97bcd	45bd6d0e-e9d6-4a1a-ae90-f5fbbcbf5682	b36d22ae-fa95-4284-8274-ee89f03b34dc	{"ar": "Beko Gas Cooker, 4 Burners, 60 cm, FSHT61111GX - Silver", "en": "No-Frost Refrigerator Beko , 367 Liters, Black- RDNE430K12B"}	{"ar": "<p>Brand: Beko</p><p>Type: Stove With Oven</p><p>Color: Silver</p><p>Matrial: Mixed</p><p>Model: Fsht61111Gx</p><p>Stand Material: Cast Iron</p><p>Digital: No</p><p>Fuel Type: Gas</p><p>Spontaneous Ignition: Yes</p><p>Oven Fan: Yes</p><p>Oven Light: Yes</p><p>Timer: Yes</p><p>Dimensions: 85 X 60 X 60 Cm</p><p>Number Of Burners: 4 Burners</p><p>Safety Feature: Yes</p><p>Auto Ignition: Yes</p>", "en": "<p>Dimension (cm)</p><p>172</p><p>Height</p><p>70</p><p>Width</p><p>65.5</p><p>Depth</p><p>Features</p><p><br /></p><p>HarvestFresh</p><p>Inspired by nature, powered by light</p><p>Vitamins in fruit and veg are no longer lost to refrigeration! HarvestFresh’s 3-colour technology mimics the 24-hour sun-cycle inside the crisper, preserving vitamins for longer. This unique technology inside your crisper will allow you to enjoy nutritious meals and a healthier lifestyle.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>NeoFrost Dual Cooling</p><p>2 separate cooling systems, no odour transfer</p><p>It’s difficult to keep the fish in the freezer together with a flavourful cake in the fridge without their odours mixing. NeoFrost Dual Cooling’s separate cooling systems for each compartment maintain ideal air flow and optimal temperatures in both the freezer and the fridge. As a result, food stays fresh for longer with no frost build-up or odour transfer.</p><p><br /></p><p>Active Odour Filter</p><p>Unwanted odours & bacteria reduced</p><p>There's nothing worse than opening the fridge door when something smells rotten inside. Thanks to a carbon filter, Active Odour Filter removes odours and bacteria from the cool air circulated in your fridge, keeping all your food nice and fresh. So no matter what you keep in your fridge, you won’t have to hold your nose when you open it.</p><p><br /></p><p>Led Illumination</p><p>Clear view of the inside</p><p>It can be tricky to see everything in your fridge, especially in the corners and at the back of selves. Led Illumination features chains of LED on the top of the fridge, and for every shelf on the side wall so you can see clearly throughout the cooler. It’s more energy-efficient that standard lighting too.</p>"}	no-frost-refrigerator-beko-367-liters-black-rdne430k12b-3080	27900.00	\N	\N	\N	0	5	active	f	0	2026-06-14 06:28:56.409	2026-06-14 06:42:04.46	\N	\N
